# Send Eidi Form 🎀

This is a simple web form that allows users to send Eidi (a traditional gift of money) by entering their name, amount, and preferred payment method.

## Features ✨
- Cute pink-themed design 🌸
- User-friendly form
- Supports multiple payment methods (JazzCash, EasyPaisa, Bank Transfer)
- Responsive layout for mobile and desktop

## How to Use 💖
1. Clone the repository:
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/your-username/eidi-form.git
   ```
2. Open `index.html` in a browser.
3. Fill in your name, amount, and select a payment method.
4. Click "Send Eidi" to get a confirmation message.

## Hosting on GitHub Pages 🚀
To make your form accessible online:
1. Go to your GitHub repository.
2. Navigate to **Settings > Pages**.
3. Under "Branch," select `main` and `/ (root)`.
4. Click **Save**, and your site will be live at `https://your-username.github.io/eidi-form/`.

